flowRoot.flowPara: The community website contains info for everyone from beginners to pros.
The teaching materials are open albeit mostly Czech.
Learn from them, contribute or fork your own course.
Come to Pyvo! Prepare a talk, even just a five-minute lightning talk. Or just come to chat. While Pivo means beer, we welcome everyone even non-drinkers.
Write an article for the Czech Python blog!
Every year, we organize a conference, PyCon CZ.
On the website you'll find past talks and current info.

text.tspan: You can find help, friends or even a job.
The Czech Python community is active and open.

flowRoot.flowPara: It's all done thanks to people like you. Formally we're pyvec.org, a nonprofit org.
